name: Ecuador's Tardis
description:
The TARDIS is an extraterrestrial spacecraft from the "Doctor Who" series that appears to be a British police call box but is much larger on the inside.

It allows the Doctor to travel through space and time, serving as a central element of his adventures.

The Tardis was placed inside of Ecuador as a token of gratitude for the Doctor Who Alliance they had prior to the construction of this Tardis.
